<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kontakt Home — Sevdiyiniz Elektronika</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        /* Ümumi Sıfırlama və Dark Mode */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #0b0b0c;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Naviqasiya Paneli (Navbar) */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 8%;
            background-color: #111113;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1c;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .logo span {
            color: #ff0022;
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: #a0a0a5;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: #ff0022;
        }

        /* Sağ tərəf: Səbət Düyməsi */
        .nav-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .cart-btn {
            background-color: #ff0022;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cart-btn:hover {
            background-color: #cc001b;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Hero / Giriş Banner Hissəsi */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 80px 8%;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .hero-left {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .hero-tag {
            background-color: #1a1a1c;
            color: #ff0022;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .hero h1 span {
            color: #ff0022;
        }
        .hero p {
            color: #a0a0a5;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .btn-red {
            background-color: #ff0022;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-red:hover {
            background-color: #cc001b;
        }
        .btn-ghost {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1c;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover {
            background-color: #1a1a1c;
            border-color: #2a2a2e;
        }

        /* Sağ tərəfdəki vizual qutu placeholder */
        .hero-right {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .hero-image-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            height: 350px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111113 0%, #1a1a1c 100%);
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2e;
            border-radius: 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 80px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">Kontakt<span>Home</span></a>
        
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/" class="active">Ana Səhifə</a></li>
            <li><a href="/mehsullar">Məhsullar</a></li>
            <li><a href="/brendler">Brendlər</a></li>
            <li><a href="/kampaniyalar">Kampaniyalar</a></li>
            <li><a href="/magazalar">Mağazalar</a></li>
            <li><a href="/kreditler">Kredit</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="nav-right">
           
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <span class="hero-tag">🔥 Yay Endirimləri — 50%-ə qədər</span>
            <h1>Ən Yaxşı <br><span>Elektronika</span><br> Bir Yerdə</h1>
            <p>Samsung, Apple, LG, Sony və daha onlarla premium brendin orijinal məhsulları indi şok nağd endirimlərlə və ya sərfəli kredit şərtləri ilə Kontakt-da!</p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="btn-red">İndi Al →</a>
                <a href="/kampaniyalar" class="btn-ghost">Kataloqa Bax</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-right">
            <div class="hero-image-placeholder">
                📱
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>